title: Unsolved Mysteries of Super Bowl LIII
itunes:title: Unsolved Mysteries of Super Bowl LIII
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal bring you the latest news in the NFL including the fallout from the Saints-Rams championship game ,(3:40) the Chiefs firing DC Bob Sutton (12:23) and Drew Brees planning to play in 2019. (24:57) Also, the NFL has announced their London game schedule. (27:43) There are many lingering questions leading up to the Super Bowl but the heroes pick out the greatest unsolved mysteries of them all. (35:00)
